thread.title: Carolyn Tortola
thread.title_full: Myprotein Italia recensione scritta da Carolyn Tortola

author: Carolyn Tortola
title: Carolyn Tortola
text: The products are good and the price is lower than most competitors without a sacrifice in quality. The shipping is quite fast and the products usually arrive well packaged. It would be helpful to have more reviews of the different flavours of proteins. It would also be helpful to have more information available about the supplements that can be taken together.
